     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xml:lang=\"fr\" lang=\"fr\"><hr/><p><b>French</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narratif généré : CarteDeConcepts FRImagingProcedureLMCDAFHIR</b></p><a name=\"FRImagingProcedureLMCDAFHIR\"> </a><a name=\"hcFRImagingProcedureLMCDAFHIR\"> </a><p>This mapping does not specify any particular context of use.</p><br/><p><b>Groupe 1 </b>Mapping de <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-lm-technique-imagerie</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-dicom-technique-imagerie</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Code source</b></td><td><b>relation</b></td><td><b>Code cible</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRLMTechniqueImagerie</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDADICOMTechniqueImagerie</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMTechniqueImagerie.identifiant</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDADICOMTechniqueImagerie.id</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMTechniqueImagerie.codeActe</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDADICOMTechniqueImagerie.code</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMTechniqueImagerie.description</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDADICOMTechniqueImagerie.text</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMTechniqueImagerie.date</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDADICOMTechniqueImagerie.effectiveTime</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMTechniqueImagerie.modaliteAcquisition</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDADICOMTechniqueImagerie.methodCode</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMTechniqueImagerie.lateralite</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDADICOMTechniqueImagerie.targetSiteCode</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMTechniqueImagerie.lateralite.precisionTopographique</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDADICOMTechniqueImagerie.targetSiteCode.qualifier</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMTechniqueImagerie.participant</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDADICOMTechniqueImagerie.participant</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Groupe 2 </b>Mapping de <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-dicom-technique-imagerie</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-procedure-imaging-document</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Code source</b></td><td><b>relation</b></td><td><b>Code cible</b></td><td><b>Commentaire</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRCDADICOMTechniqueImagerie</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRProcedureImagingDocument</td><td/></tr><tr><td>FRCDADICOMTechniqueImagerie.id</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRProcedureImagingDocument.identifier</td><td/></tr><tr><td>FRCDADICOMTechniqueImagerie.code</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRProcedureImagingDocument.code</td><td/></tr><tr><td>FRCDADICOMTechniqueImagerie.text</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRProcedureImagingDocument.note</td><td/></tr><tr><td>FRCDADICOMTechniqueImagerie.effectiveTime</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRProcedureImagingDocument.performed[x]</td><td/></tr><tr><td>FRCDADICOMTechniqueImagerie.methodCode</td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #efefef\">(not mapped)</td><td style=\"background-color: #efefef\">Pas de correspondance directe dans FRProcedureImagingDocument pour la modalité d’acquisition. Cette donnée est incluse dans le profil FRImagingStudyDocument.modality.</td></tr><tr><td>FRCDADICOMTechniqueImagerie.targetSiteCode</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRProcedureImagingDocument.bodySite</td><td/></tr><tr><td>FRCDADICOMTechniqueImagerie.targetSiteCode.qualifier</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td/><td/></tr><tr><td>FRCDADICOMTechniqueImagerie.participant</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td/><td/></tr></table></div>"
